title: fx64_f23
description:
http://www.fx64.net - fx64 linux f23

FX64 Linux is a Fedora 23 based distro.
Google Chrome, Java IcedTea, Adobe Flash Player, Skype & RAR preinstalled.

Hand picked essential system, office, multimedia and internet applications. Updates directly from the official Fedora, RPM Fusion and Adobe repositories. Comes with Gnome, Cinnamon and Fluxbox. Thousands of free applications for every need directly from the open source community.

Clean, lean and feature rich FREE AS IN BEER experience!
